  - Layer 3 (endings): 3-4 endings with is_ending=true and ending_text
  - Use `enable_npc` calls on 2-3 nodes to dramatically introduce hidden NPCs
  - Use tag conditions to create mutually exclusive branching paths
  - 12-15 nodes total

